The '''2020 [[European Junior and U23 Canoe Slalom Championships]]''' will take place in [[Solkan]], [[Slovenia]] from 13 to 16 August 2020 under the auspices of the [[European Canoe Association]] (ECA).<ref>{{cite web|title=2020 ECA Junior&U23 Canoe Slalom European Championships|url=https://www.canoe-europe.org/calendar/2020-eca-junior-u23-canoe-slalom-european-championships-55|website=Canoe-Europe.org|accessdate=24 February 2018}}</ref> It will be the 22nd edition of the competition for Juniors (U18) and the 18th edition for the Under 23 category.
