{{Infobox football club | clubname = Child Restoration Outreach Football Club | founded = | ground = [[Mbale Municipal Stadium]] | league = [[Ugandan Super League]] | season = 2013–14 | position = 16th }}
'''Child Restoration Outreach Football Club''' or simply '''CRO FC''' is a [[association football|football]] club in [[Mbale]], [[Uganda]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/tableso/oeg08.html |title=Uganda 2007/08 |website=Rsssf.com |date=2010-08-27 |accessdate=2016-04-03}}</ref> They play in the top level of Ugandan professional football, the [[Ugandan Super League]]. They were relegated in 2008. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/associations/association=uga/nationalleague/standings.html |title=FUFA Super League 2015-2016 |website=Fifa.com |accessdate=2016-04-03}}</ref> [[Mbale Municipal Stadium]] is their home stadium, it has a capacity of 10,000.
