The '''Comité de Football des Îles du Nord''' is the official [[football (soccer)]] federation of the French half of the island of [[Collectivity of Saint Martin|Saint Martin]] and [[Saint Barthélemy]] island, although Saint Barthélemy now has its own [[Comité de Football de Saint Barthélemy]] [http://www.journal-officiel.gouv.fr/association/index.php?ctx=eJxtjEEKAjEMAPOU0g80CB70qnjyuPdSa6SBtFnTruCTfIcfc*G8xxmGiQIPg*hqkHrXDPEJWW1WS4PCMKKjn3QOJ73TVKhSQDwgonduK7syLWfKklbP2kJP3EZNNrg594fbCuX7Eapvv7XwEAuPyyICuz38AAJRN3A_&page=4&JTH_ID=009000&JAN_LIEU_DECL=saintmartin%20%20saintbarth%E9lemy (Journaux Officiels)].

