'''Haras du Petit Tellier''' is one of the oldest [[thoroughbred]] [[horse breeding]] farms in [[France]]. Located on 1.45&nbsp;km² at [[Sévigny]], [[Orne]] in the [[Lower Normandy]] region, the business was founded in 1850 and is today run by the founder's descendant, Patrick Chedeville.
==References== * [http://www.petittellier.com/ Haras du Petit Tellier official website] (English - French - German languages)
