'''Lithuanian Snowboarding Championships''' (lt. - ''Lietuvos snieglenčių sporto čempionatas'') is open national championship of [[snowboarding]] in Lithuania, which was established in 2011.
== Rules == Championship is made from three parts. In every of three stage top 10 snowboarders get points from 10 to 1. Person who gets the most points after 3 stages won the national championship.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.snowarena.lt/lt/apie_mus/naujienos?Events_page_nr%3D0%26Events_item_id%3D50 |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2011-02-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722153039/http://www.snowarena.lt/lt/apie_mus/naujienos?Events_page_nr=0&Events_item_id=50 |archivedate=2011-07-22 |df= }}</ref>
